Welcome to Aspen.
This mud is in it's early development stages. It was started in early 2009 by Tyler Littlefield, and has slowly progressed to what you see now.
Feel free to create yourself a char (via supplying new as your player name), and join us.
We are always looking for feedback and positive suggestions on how we might make this mud a better place for everyone.
Please report all new suggestions via the Idea command.
